<% content_for :page_title, "About Us" %>

<p class="staff__lead">
  A Touch of Tranquility Spa is a sanctuary for restorative health; as a holistic spa for massage therapy, skin care, and expert hair removal services.
</p>
<p>
  Our facility was established in 2003.
  We are a specified-treatment-oriented, therapeutic wellness spa.
  We are staffed by NYS licensed professionals with over 25 years of combined experience and we continue to educate ourselves in all areas of expertise.
</p>
<p>
  Our philosophy is: to educate and treat the whole you; to help you heal from the inside out; with massage as a medical therapy for injury and pain management,
  rejuvenation massage, signature bodywork as a truly relaxing, unique, organic and healing experience, to holistic nutrition education all the way to expert
  waxing service and healing skin imbalances with superb care and education, all designed around your specific needs.
</p>
<p>
  By way of this philosophy we can encourage and support you through healthful, mindful decisions leading to better health happiness and well-being.
</p>

<div class="staff-grid category">
  <h1 class="category__header">Our Staff</h1>
  <% collection.each_slice(3) do |staff_chunk| %>
    <div class="staff-grid__item staff__row">
      <% staff_chunk.each do |staff| %>
        <div class="staff__col-sm-4">
          <div class="staff__photo">
            <%= link_to(staff, :class => "staff__link") do %>
              <%= image_tag(staff.photo.url, :class => "staff__image--grid staff--img-responsive staff--img-rounded", :alt => "#{staff.first_name} #{staff.last_name}") %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <h2 class="staff__name"><%= staff.first_name %> <%= staff.last_name %></h2>
          <div class="staff__credentials"><%= staff.credentials %></div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

